      "span_text": "A similar retrospective analysis on data collected between February and June 2007 at a large referral medical center in Alabama led to different findings. Primary end points were duration of antibiotic therapy, length of hospital stay, total stay in the intensive care unit, total cost of hospitalization, and adverse antibiotic events."
